{"tid":2158362,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"要破局就要議會戰線國際化！","createTime":"2020-08-15T16:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T11:36:06.000Z","uid":22822,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a2a3cbd34a0bc631bbb3d361554c8ff0003fe643","tid":2158362,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:14:01.000Z","msg":"中共今次識玩，佢知道泛民係初選收咗皮，本土抬頭。呢個局面對於中共同埋民主派都唔係一件好事，所以佢轉守為攻，將立法會選舉押後一年，然後由原班人馬上，只要泛民應承參與，咁一個有反對派嘅議會就完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">局己成形，要破局就要諗點&quot;play out of the book&quot;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n初選係一個有60萬民意基礎嘅選舉，贏咗嘅人有無諗過點樣利用黎個身份係國際空間游走？"},{"pid":"993fb585d732a609b5cd6bd7b3f9f555f57434ca","tid":2158362,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:21:46.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1494f3e31ddd350a927a7b8f30c0223268e14c9b","tid":2158362,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:32:10.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4b1cf82842c21fc9dac01c7112b4279e980c32da","tid":2158362,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T22:26:07.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n傳北戴河定調「三軟三硬」 習近平被迫棄戰狼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2158652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2158652</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"09a3fe62d71bdfcee962e3aacaf2cee94c224eff","tid":2158362,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T22:30:00.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fa120075b0dde89e0fc91a454a0c205ff6137fe2","tid":2158362,"uid":249979,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T02:35:38.000Z","msg":"而家最緊要既國際戰線<br />\n全部都係靠本土抗爭派同流亡手足<br />\n泛民乜撚都冇做過<br />\n仲配合中共叫國際唔好制裁香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左保份糧真係乜撚都做得出"},{"pid":"a14bac31fc18492bbcaaf620e672d08d5c85430b","tid":2158362,"uid":249979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T02:37:26.000Z","msg":"97前同而家都係啦<br />\n每次到左最重要既決擇時機<br />\n泛民每次都係選擇保自己利益, 出賣香港<br />\nDKLMCH"},{"pid":"1f7b2c1b42dd868cce17b18f0bf1b851752cd355","tid":2158362,"uid":249979,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T02:44:11.000Z","msg":"佢地班老泛民 呢一年來完全冇參與過街頭抗爭落過前線<br />\n根本就係&quot;志不同 不相為謀&quot;<br />\n而家局勢對香港人大好 國際撐香港人<br />\n破舊立新既黃金機會<br />\n主力要全攻國際戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n制裁晒中共+港共+臨立會受任議員"},{"pid":"517d90734d0f6d5e9c7dd2bf466d56e4ae8934d6","tid":2158362,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T02:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5722315aa642da6180238b70871976dd5137f405","tid":2158362,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c473aaa1625e0b2d7ff973607a00f15623f18b","tid":2158362,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:30:48.000Z","msg":"破局要有甲午戰爭 中興會 同盟會 果D先得"},{"pid":"86a97ce221d3d2daf8872c95a4a2a23b1ef7adf6","tid":2158362,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:31:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7f566c41f264a312e1de5aa58fc3fc26987515d9","tid":2158362,"uid":54946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:33:21.000Z","msg":"唔通想學英國搞影子議會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505c45ebaab7320f6b797a25a773534dd2f58ab4","tid":2158362,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:15:44.000Z","msg":"所有泛民都應該杯葛立會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 杯葛立會使其失去合法性，區選已證明大多數人支持泛民。<br />\n2. 人民授權4年期限已到，臨時立會有人民授權係歪理。<br />\n3. 人大委任是非法，國際亦認同，泛民不應配合中央歪曲基本法。<br />\n4. 留守立會抗爭空間已不存在，聯合區議員成立「影子議會」議政。<br />\n5. 為下屆選舉爭取籌碼，如果下屆再DQ議員，泛民繼續杯葛。<br />\n6. 北京明顯派人放風希望泛民參加，如果泛民唔參加，等同開綠燈比美國制裁臨時立會議員、香港政府必定迎來更激烈嘅制裁。"},{"pid":"dba973799a4d7e7e185f16afa95a6689f9d00b6c","tid":2158362,"uid":271601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:07:36.000Z","msg":"我就話全部入返立會，做返一直做嘅嘢，等共產黨炒魷。炒魷咪就係最勁嘅國際宣傳囉。"},{"pid":"33df176a04e07867cf37c4dcc5a9fdd18307c204","tid":2158362,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:36:06.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}